Barbero M(1), Falla D(2), Clijsen R(3), Ghirlanda F(4), Schneebeli A(4), Ernst 
MJ(5), Cescon C(4).

Author information:
(1)Rehabilitation Research Laboratory 2rLab, Department of Business Economics, 
Health and Social Care, University of Applied Sciences and Arts of Southern 
Switzerland, Manno, Switzerland. Electronic address: marco.barbero@supsi.ch.
(2)Centre of Precision Rehabilitation for Spinal Pain (CPR Spine), School of 
Sport, Exercise and Rehabilitation Sciences, College of Life and Environmental 
Sciences, University of Birmingham, UK.
(3)Department of Business Economics, Health and Social Care, University of 
